            "type": "text_panel",
            "width": 0.22,
            "height": 28,
            "content_type": "code_chars",
            "chars": "01アイオス♦◆▲△○●◉⬡⬢∴∵∶∷∸∹∺∻∼∽∾∿≀ ΦΨΛΣΘΩ∞≠≡≢≣≤≥≦≧",
